  G|-7~~~---|  
  D|-7~~~---|  
  A|--------|  
  E|--------|]  
  *Riff 1 (Main)*  
  *(P = palm mute briefly before changing chord)*  
  *( x = left hand mute and strike strings)*  
  *note: 9-P means play 9th position, hold and then mute*  
    *9P mean play 9th position and then mute*  
